title: Kitchenaid Counter Depth Refrigerator KRFC704FBS Tour
description:
In this video we take a look inside the Kitchen Aid KRFC704FBS refrigerator.  For more information or to place an order please visit us at Abt.com: http://www.abt.com/product/102179/KitchenAid-23.8-Cu.-Ft.-Black-Stainless-Steel-Counter-Depth-French-Door-Refrigerator-KRFC704FBS.html?utm_source=youtube&utm_medium=video&utm_campaign=KRFC704FBS_20170426 

Features:
- Under-Shelf Prep Zone
- Slide-Away Split Shelf
- Full-Extension FreshSeal™ Crispers
- Full-Extension Custom Temperature-Controlled Pantry Drawer
- Full-Extension Pull Out Tray
- Preserva® Food Care System with Linear Compressor
- 3-Tier Freezer Drawer with Extend-Freeze Setting
- In-Door-Ice® System
- Panoramic LED Lighting
- PrintShield™ Finish
- Platinum Interior Design with Premium Wood Finish Accents
- Professionally-Inspired Design
- Exterior Ice and Water Dispenser
- FreshSeal™ Herb Storage
- Adjustable Spill Resistant Shelves
- Removable Door Bins with Metal Accents
- FreshSeal™ Dairy Bin
- Measured and Favorite Water Fill
- Energy Star® Certified
